snippet.title: Aquanaute - Thomson MO/TO Gameplay
snippet.description:
Released for the Thomson MO6 to TO8 models by FIL in 1987, your aim in this French game is to explore the ocean to find ancient treasures. But beware of mines, sharks, and other dangers!

Developed by Bruno Ouachée
Published by France Image Logiciel (FIL)

#fil #aquanaute #thomsonmoto #retrogaming #retrogames #theforeseenarcade
